###################################################################
# This is a python routine, ready for running on a linux machine. #
# It can not be run on windows if Hebrew is used in some of the   #
# names. Windows can not seem to handle the discrepency!          #
#-----------------------------------------------------------------#
# This does require an excel spread sheet called:                 #
#         MishBerech.xlsx                                         #
#     set up as follows:                                          #
# Column 1: Blank                                                 #
# Column 2: Addressee (email)                                     #
# Column 3: Person who needs the MishBerech                       #
# Column 4: Date in dd-MMM-yy format (e.g. 28-Aug-15)             #
#           We keep this as the 'date requested' and we keep      #
#           saying the mishBerech for 45 days. Then we send       #
#           an email to check on the choleh and change the date.  #
# Column 5: comments (ignored)                                    #
# Column 6: Email Address                                         #
###################################################################
